about.summary: Contains various routines for drawing ellipses and ellipse-like confidence regions, implementing the plots described in Murdoch and Chow (1996), A graphical display of large correlation matrices, The American Statistician 50, 178-180. There are also routines implementing the profile plots described in Bates and Watts (1988), Nonlinear Regression Analysis and its Applications.

name: r-ellipse
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.4.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-ellipse
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: ellipse_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ellipse_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ellipse/ellipse_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1a9a9c52195b26c2b4d51ad159ab98aff7aa8ca25fdc6b2198818d1a0adb023d

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1003
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ellipse')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ellipse')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ellipse
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Contains various routines for drawing ellipses and ellipse-like confidence regions,
    implementing the plots described in Murdoch and Chow (1996), A graphical display
    of large correlation matrices, The American Statistician 50, 178-180. There are
    also routines implementing the profile plots described in Bates and Watts (1988),
    Nonlinear Regression Analysis and its Applications.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.0
